write_up: After You is the only leak on this list. I wouldn’t have included it, first-draft mumbled verses and all, if I didn’t still think it was a finished artistic product in a way. He can reinterpret this again if he wants but I don’t even know if it would still have the same sort of emotional power he gets across here from freestyling. Sometimes, when the productions perfect, talented artists can catch something real from somewhere inside you as you invent on the spot. Being alone with yourself and your voice and your thoughts is enough.
lyric: You know the evil that men do
